Hi! I'm Harpreet Singh and welcome to my little corner of the internet. I'm currently a graduate student in Trinity College Dublin's [SCSS department](https://www.scss.tcd.ie/) where I'm focusing on [Networks and Distributed Systems](https://www.scss.tcd.ie/postgraduate/mscnds/).
